{% extends '@AppBundle/Resources/Email/base.txt.twig' %}
{% block body %}
Welcome {{ policy.user.name }}.

**
------------------------------------------------------------
Thank you for joining so-sure.  We're excited to have you onboard.

Your policy is for {{ policy.phone }} and runs from {{ policy.start|date }} to {{ policy.end|date }}.

We've also attached a copy of all your key documents, including your policy terms for reference. If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us (support@wearesosure.com).

{% if policy.promoCode != 'launch' %}
Want up to 80% of your money back?

For each friend that also buys insurance, we'll add up to £{{ policy.connectionValue }} to your Reward Pot (we'll also do the same for them).

Connect with {{ policy.maxConnections }} friends and provided none of you make a claim you'll get 80% of your money back at the end of the year.
{% else %}
Want your insurance for free?

As one of first 1,000 customers, we'd like to reward you! For each friend that also buys insurance, we'll add up to {{ policy.connectionValue }} to your Reward Pot (rather than the usual £10).

Connect with {{ policy.maxConnections }} friends and provided none of you make a claim you'll get all your money back at the end of the year!
{% endif %}
{% endblock body %}
